CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 25, 1959, pg.14 reads: "Tax Lein Department - Left to right: Olga Berggren, clerk; Vincent A. Smith, special utility clerk; James P. Drummond, clerk investigator; Joseph Ofcinik, utility clerk; Elizabeth Jones clerk, and John M. Nalitz, cashier-check."
TitMainTitle: Interior of tax lein department of Allegheny County Prothonotary office with Olga Berggren, Vincent A. Smith, James P. Drummond, Joseph Ofcinik, Elizabeth Jones, and John M. Nalitz, working at desks, Lawyer's Title Company and Mellon Bank calendars on wall
